    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3. This specimen features the legendary S54B32 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies and an 8,000 RPM redline. The Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission provides tactile engagement, paired with a factory Variable M Differential Lock for optimal corner-exit traction. This example has undergone comprehensive preventative maintenance, including a complete VANOS overhaul, rod bearing replacement, and structural subframe reinforcement. The chassis remains taut with refreshed bushings and OEM dampers, preserving its celebrated handling dynamics. Finished in pristine paint with an immaculate interior, this is a turn-key collector-quality icon.",
      "price": 47500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
